  <!-- Terms modal -->
  <div class="overlay" id="overlay" role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
    <div class="modal">
      <div class="modalHeader">
        <strong>Valentine Terms & Conditions (37 pages)</strong>
        <button class="closeX" id="closeModal" aria-label="Close">‚úï</button>
      </div>

      <div class="modalBody">
        <div class="tcBox" id="tcBox">
          <p><b>Important:</b> To select ‚ÄúNo‚Äù, you must read and agree to all terms below.</p>
          <p>1. ‚ÄúNo‚Äù is defined as ‚ÄúYes‚Äù, but with extra steps.</p>
          <p>2. Attempting ‚ÄúNo‚Äù may cause spontaneous affection, smiling, and/or plans being made for dinner.</p>
          <p>3. User acknowledges that the creator is extremely cute and will continue being cute regardless of button choice.</p>
          <p>4. Any clicks on ‚ÄúNo‚Äù will be interpreted as ‚ÄúI‚Äôm joking‚Äù.</p>
          <p>5. You agree to a minimum of one hug (or equivalent cuddle credits) upon confirmation.</p>
          <p>6. You agree that you are the best thing that happened to me.</p>
          <p>7. You agree that this website is legally binding in the Court of Love‚Ñ¢.</p>
          <p>8. You agree that scrolling is mandatory.</p>
          <p>9. You agree that the ‚ÄúNo‚Äù option may shrink due to supply chain issues.</p>
          <p>10. You agree to more dates, more laughs, and more us.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:12px; opacity:0.75;">
            Keep scrolling. There are definitely 37 pages. Totally.
          </p>
          <div style="height:900px;"></div>
          <p><b>End of Terms.</b> You may now attempt ‚ÄúNo‚Äù (good luck).</p>
        </div>

        <p id="scrollNote" style="margin:10px 0 0; font-size:12.5px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);">
          Scroll to the bottom to enable ‚ÄúI Agree‚Äù.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="modalFooter">
        <button class="secondary" id="cancelModal">Cancel</button>
        <button class="primary" id="agreeBtn" disabled>I Agree</button>
